title: Swirl Couple On Steve Wilkos Goes Off Rails When The Man Hits His Baby Momma [Video]
text:
Here's the moment that has everyone talking. #SteveWilkos pic.twitter.com/5jOlJ0v5Qw 
— depressed knicks fan (@kev_chillen) February 21, 2017 

This incident is being talked about everywhere for the simple fact “Cortez” hit his girlfriend on TV! Steve Wilkos’ show is known for having messy breakups, so a domestic violence incident playing out on the show is cliche, but this is the first time we are seeing a man hit a girl back like this.
